					<description><![CDATA[I wish that it were easier to remember when to capitalize things like this. It gets so confusing. capitalize months and days of the week, but not seasons? They all tell us an amount of time. It seems that seasons should be capitalized. but that&#039;s just my opinion.]]></description>
			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>I wish that it were easier to remember when to capitalize things like this. It gets so confusing. capitalize months and days of the week, but not seasons? They all tell us an amount of time. It seems that seasons should be capitalized. but that&#8217;s just my opinion.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
		
